data.description: 4.6 acres of quiet, peaceful country living. Welcome to your new home! It's a special place - not just for anyone. This charming, single level home offers you the best in country living. Lots of spacious acres ready for your creative ideas ( pool, garden, Pickle ball ). Imagine having coffee in the morning or you favorite drink watching the sun rise or set. This 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home features a front entrance foyer with Formal Dining Room to the right and Formal Living room to the left. All have hardwood floors. The Great Room features a large, cozy fireplace, Dura Ceramic tile floors and deck access. The spacious kitchen has lots of cabinets/storage, Bay Window, eat-in and DC tile floors. The laundry room and 1/2 bath are in the hall to the 2 car garage. The Master Suite, located in the back of the home, has a walk-in closet and Master Bath. There are two additional bedrooms. The backyard (acres) provides plenty of room for recreation and the spacious deck is perfect for entertaining and grilling. There is a 20 x12 storage shed and Pole Barn for additional equipment. This home allows for easy access to Fort Jackson, VA Hospital, I-77 and I-20 for dining or shopping at the malls or Downtown Columbia. A must see home.
